sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HTTPApi as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8000/TCP HTTP (OpenAI)
    participant GRPCApi as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC (TGIS)
    participant VLLMEngine as vLLM Engine
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre<br/>Accelerator
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)

    Note over VLLMEngine,Storage: Model Loading (Startup)
    VLLMEngine->>Storage: Load model weights<br/>(volume mount / storage API)
    Storage-->>VLLMEngine: Model artifacts

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 1: HTTP/OpenAI Inference
    Client->>KubeRBAC: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KubeRBAC->>HTTPApi: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>Auth validated
    HTTPApi->>VLLMEngine: Inference request
    VLLMEngine->>Spyre: Accelerated compute<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>VLLMEngine: Computation result
    VLLMEngine-->>HTTPApi: Generated tokens
    HTTPApi-->>KubeRBAC: JSON response
    KubeRBAC-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS/8443

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 2: gRPC/TGIS Inference
    Client->>KubeRBAC: GenerationService RPC<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KubeRBAC->>GRPCApi: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033<br/>Auth validated
    GRPCApi->>VLLMEngine: Inference request
    VLLMEngine->>Spyre: Accelerated compute<br/>Hardware interface
    Spyre-->>VLLMEngine: Computation result
    VLLMEngine-->>GRPCApi: Generated tokens
    GRPCApi-->>KubeRBAC: gRPC response
    KubeRBAC-->>Client: gRPC response<br/>HTTPS/8443

    Note over Client,Spyre: Alternative: Istio Service Mesh Path
    Client->>HTTPApi: POST /v1/completions<br/>mTLS (Istio STRICT)<br/>Service Identity
    HTTPApi->>VLLMEngine: Inference request
    VLLMEngine->>Spyre: Accelerated compute
    Spyre-->>VLLMEngine: Result
    VLLMEngine-->>HTTPApi: Generated tokens
    HTTPApi-->>Client: JSON response<br/>mTLS
